PID: New participant IDs generated to maintain anonymity
integ1: "This person is has a great deal of integrity." (1=strongly disagree, 7=strongly agree)
integ2: "I can trust this person's word." (1=strongly disagree, 7=strongly agree)
integ3: "This person cares about honesty and truth." (1=strongly disagree, 7=strongly agree)
legality_self: "Do you think [issue] should be legal or illegal?" (1=legal, 2=illegal)
care_self: "How strongly do you care about whether or not [issue] should be legal (regardless of your stance on the issue)?" (1=not at all, 5=extremely)
libcon: "Do you consider yourself to be more liberal or conservative?" (1=definitely liberal, 7=definitely conservative)
demrep: "Do you consider yourself to be more of a Democrat or a Republican?" (1=definitely a democrat, 7=definitely a republican)
match: Whether or not participants agreed with target (based on "stance" and "legality_self" agreement)
